# Frontend Standards

## Stack

- React
- TypeScript
- Vite
- React Router
- TanStack Query

## Architecture

Use feature-based frontend architecture.

## Feature Structure

features/
  todos/
    api/
    components/
    hooks/
    pages/
    types/

## State Management

- Prefer server state with TanStack Query.
- Avoid global state unless necessary.

## Components

- Keep components small.
- Prefer composition over inheritance.
- Separate smart and dumb components.

## Styling

- Use TailwindCSS.
- Avoid inline styles.

## API Calls

- Centralize HTTP client configuration.
- Use typed responses.

